						               													<description>With this very first expansion you will be able to add meteorological events to your battles. Its use is extremely simple but will bring a great replayability forcing players to anticipate or being surprised by some unexpected weather changes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At the beginig of a game, put 4 meteo cards face down next to the timeline. Each card will have an influence on the 6 time spaces next to it.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Then, the first card is flipped face up and the battle can begin. The other cards will be flipped as soon as a player enter their area. when both players have left an area, the corresponding card is replaced by another from the meteo pile face down.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     The rain: when you start your turn in this area, spend 2h to activate a troop card instead of 1h.&amp;#10;     Sun shine: when you start your turn in this area, play your turn normally.&amp;#10;     Smog: when you start your turn in this area, during a combat, you skip the shooting phase.&amp;#10;     Storm: when you start your turn in this area, you can only play your clan cards face down.&amp;#10;     Snow: when you start your turn in this area, discard 1 troop card in each of your assault area.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;user summary&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
